&lt;p&gt;xcloner,3.53,Other&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Developer statement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="entry clearfix label-warning"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;Today we have made available a new release — version 3.5.4 — for the unmaintained Joomla version of XCloner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;Prior versions of XCloner for Joomla contained an Authenticated Local File Disclosure vulnerability that has been patched in the latest version.&nbsp;Any users of the unmaintained XCloner for Joomla package should upgrade immediately.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;Details of the exploit have not been published to allow users time to upgrade.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

